div.p:
. . . I, the Lord, knowing the calamity which should come upon the inhabitants of the earth,
called upon my servant Joseph Smith, Jun., and spake unto him from heaven, and gave him
commandments;

Behold, I tell you these things even as I also told the people of the destruction of Jerusalem;
and my word shall be verified at this time as it hath hitherto been verified
(D&C 5:19-20).
